        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "Beloved son, brother, grandson,  uncle ,  brother in-law, nephew  and friend",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -110.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "We walk this path with with an empty hand a heart that aches, a soul unmanned.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -239.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "Each step a whisper, a quiet refrain, missing you deeply through joy and pain",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -128.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "The world feels quieter, the days stretch long, your absence the shadow in every song",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -28
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "The stars hold your voice the wind carries your name yet nothing can ever feel quiet the same",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -145
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "RICHARDSON",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 40,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -174
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "I hold  onto the moments  the love that we knew",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -257.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "The  laughter , the warmth, the essence  of you",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 24.893,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -50.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "Each memory a lantern that lights our way through the darkest night to a brighter day",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -275.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "But oh how we long for the day we&apos;ll meet where time and space can no longer cheat",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -292
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "Where arms will hold what was once apart and love will mend our fractured hearts",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -73
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "align": "center",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "So until that day our hearts will yearn for the place where the stars and our souls return",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_mm": 18,
          "weight": 400
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -203.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
